00:00:12,371 --> 00:00:15,811
♪Have you ever heard about♪

2
00:00:15,811 --> 00:00:18,691
♪The cliff of a snow mountain♪

3
00:00:19,211 --> 00:00:24,331
♪Once fascinated numerous people?♪

4
00:00:26,011 --> 00:00:29,251
♪Legend has it that♪

5
00:00:29,251 --> 00:00:32,051
♪There were treasures at the peak♪

6
00:00:32,891 --> 00:00:37,971
♪But also there was a bottomless chasm
hidden over there♪

7
00:00:39,571 --> 00:00:43,011
♪The smart, the fool♪

8
00:00:43,051 --> 00:00:45,851
♪And the kind people♪

9
00:00:46,491 --> 00:00:52,331
♪All are familiar to you♪

10
00:00:53,211 --> 00:00:56,771
♪On the mountainside, on the cliff♪

11
00:00:57,091 --> 00:00:59,691
♪On the cloud♪

12
00:01:00,091 --> 00:01:05,211
♪And in the human world♪

13
00:01:17,051 --> 00:01:24,331
♪Snowflakes are drifting profusely and disorderly♪

14
00:01:36,091 --> 00:01:40,091
=Joy of Life Special Edition=

15
00:01:40,091 --> 00:01:43,011
=Episode 14=

16
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:44,879
One more thing.

17
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,599
According to the information
sent from Beiqi,

18
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,319
my son was caught

19
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,799
because his identity was disclosed.

20
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,799
By secret agents from Beiqi?

21
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,879
No, not from Beiqi.

22
00:01:57,959 --> 00:02:00,120
You mean from the capital city?

23
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:04,079
He was betrayed by someone
from the capital city.

24
00:02:04,319 --> 00:02:05,400
Bingyun lurking in Beiqi

25
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,120
is a top secret.

26
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:07,159
Besides His Majesty,

27
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:07,680
only officials from

28
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,759
our Investigator's Office know it.

29
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,680
Can it be someone from our office?

30
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,919
Why not?

31
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,280
Head,

32
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,080
I think we should carry out

33
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,319
a thorough investigation right away.

34
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:17,319
No need.

35
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:19,240
It's a serious problem.

36
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,400
It ends now.

37
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,199
Never mention it again.

38
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:24,919
Yes.

39
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,879
The Investigator's Office has
been established for so many years.

40
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:35,520
Time passes so quickly.

41
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,439
It's time to replace some old stuff.

42
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,039
Dad, you want to see me.

43
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:53,520
You're back.

44
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,560
Come and take a seat.

45
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,400
The negotiation

46
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,439
in Court of State Ceremonials is over.

47
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:04,199
Be cautious at the Hall tomorrow.

48
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,039
You mean

49
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:07,800
the banquet tomorrow night?

50
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,919
What's wrong?

51
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,000
you're elegant and kind.

52
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:18,280
literary giants are all in Beiqi.

53
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,639
In earlier years,

54
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,919
scholars actually found it an honor

55
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:24,479
to pass
the imperial examinations in Beiqi.

56
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,719
Though things are better these years,

57
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,599
when it comes to scholars,

58
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,919
Nanqing is no match to Beiqi.

59
00:03:32,159 --> 00:03:35,840
Now the Nanqing literary circles

60
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,120
have anchored their hopes on you.

61
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:40,759
I...

62
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:43,080
The literary circles?

63
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,639
Zhuang Mohan and his mission

64
00:03:46,039 --> 00:03:47,800
"A thousand miles from home, I'm grieved at
autumn's plight" which you wrote a few days ago

65
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:49,120
is rated as
the No.1 Current Seven-character Poem

66
00:03:49,319 --> 00:03:51,680
by scholars of Nanqing.

67
00:03:53,879 --> 00:03:55,879
Many say in private that

68
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:58,520
accomplished at such a young age,

69
00:03:58,919 --> 00:04:01,800
you can be better
than Zhuang Mohan in future.

70
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,439
I just wrote one poem.

71
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,560
They are too hasty
in drawing the conclusion.

72
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,639
One poem is not much,

73
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,439
but we've longed for a talented scholar

74
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,120
for so long.

75
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:14,080
We may even fight a losing battle.

76
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:15,560
Who will lose?

77
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:17,399
You, of course.

78
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,560
So tomorrow night,

79
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,439
everyone will watch me

80
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:25,680
meeting the literary giant

81
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:26,879
Zhuang Mohan.

82
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:30,360
You don't need to be amazing.

83
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:33,279
Just play it safe.

84
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,199
That's enough.

85
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,279
Will you go tomorrow night?

86
00:04:40,279 --> 00:04:41,639
The banquet tomorrow

87
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:43,879
is especially set for
Court of State Ceremonials

88
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:45,240
and Board of Rites.

89
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,839
I'm the Assistant Minister
of Ministry of Revenue.

90
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,000
Why would I go?

91
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,000
Don't worry.

92
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:54,600
Just a little advice.

93
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,600
Respected as Zhuang Mohan is,

94
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,439
why would he actually
make things difficult

95
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:01,120
for a young man like you?

96
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:43,120
Fan Xian will also attend
the banquet tomorrow night.

97
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:46,839
Master Zhuang, please ruin his name.

98
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:08,319
You've hung up a red lantern.

99
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:11,720
Uncle, for all these years,

100
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:13,279
I've been wondering

101
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,040
whether you can see or not.

102
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:16,399
How come you know

103
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:16,920
I hang up a lantern?

104
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,120
And you even know the color.

105
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,279
It's hard for me to explain.

106
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,480
I can know everything.

107
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,360
But I don't see with eyes.

108
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:28,800
You see with your heart.

109
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,839
I don't know how to put it.

110
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:34,120
Uncle...

111
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,480
I find you mysterious all the time.

112
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,639
If anyone dares to piss you off,

113
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:39,120
he's definitely dice with death.

114
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,319
Take a seat. Take a seat. Take a seat.

115
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,199
Let's get down to business.

116
00:06:52,839 --> 00:06:53,600
Tomorrow night,

117
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,360
the imperial family will hold a banquet at
the Hall of Prayer for Good Harvest.

118
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:56,639
The Hall of Prayer for Good Harvest?

119
00:06:57,519 --> 00:06:58,839
How is Wang Qinian involved?

120
00:06:59,319 --> 00:06:59,720
Who?

121
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,959
Wang Qinian,

122
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,480
Uncle,

123
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:06,120
besides being mysterious,

124
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,240
how come your thoughts

125
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,079
are so hard to follow recently?

126
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,759
Thoughts?

127
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:16,600
I don't think
the Hall of Prayer for Good Harvest

128
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,639
has anything to do with Wang Qinian.

129
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:19,319
Fine.

130
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,639
Let's get down to business.

131
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,639
The banquet tomorrow is mainly for

132
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:26,000
the celebration of finishing
the war against Beiqi.

133
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:27,959
It's kind of a big event.

134
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,360
Aren't you going to ask me

135
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,399
why I ask you over?

136
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,160
Aren't you going to tell me
if I don't ask?

137
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,639
You've made a point.

138
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:40,839
Fine.

139
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,240
After the banquet tomorrow night,

140
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,560
we'll break into the imperial harem.

141
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,480
Are you sure?

142
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:48,240
Everyone will relax

143
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,240
after a great event.

144
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,360
OK, the plan remains unchanged.

145
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,120
I'll lure Hong Sixiang away,

146
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:54,560
and you should sneak into
the Empress Dowager's palace

147
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,439
to find the key.

148
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,680
There's one last problem.

149
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:57,959
I don't know

150
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,079
where the Empress Dowager keeps the key.

151
00:07:59,519 --> 00:08:01,519
It might take time to find it.

152
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,519
There's a secret compartment

153
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,800
on the bed board under her pillow.

154
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:07,279
All her important things are kept there.

155
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:08,839
How did you know

156
00:08:09,879 --> 00:08:11,079
Your mom searched it before.

157
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:13,560
Why did my mom

158
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,360
search her secret compartment?

159
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:19,240
The old lady has lived in widowhood
for so many years.

160
00:08:19,879 --> 00:08:21,160
Though she looks serious,

161
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,680
I wonder whether she keeps

162
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,319
love letters in private or not.

163
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,399
Those are the words
said by your mom back then.

164
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:32,679
So she searched the Empress Dowager's

165
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:34,840
secret compartment only for gossiping!

166
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,600
I've no idea

167
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,639
what gossiping implies,

168
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,759
but yes, you're right.

169
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,960
Didn't she get caught?

170
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,480
I kept watch for her.

171
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:48,720
Why are you laughing?

172
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,240
Words can't express

173
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,600
my feelings right now.

174
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,039
What feelings?

175
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:56,039
Just forget it.

176
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,720
Anyway, back then,

177
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:58,399
my mom had solved

178
00:08:58,399 --> 00:08:59,279
the biggest problem for me.

179
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:00,320
Now,

180
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:02,600
as long as I know where the key is,

181
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:04,240
I feel quite sure of getting it out.

182
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,120
If we take the key,

183
00:09:06,679 --> 00:09:07,879
the old lady might notice.

184
00:09:08,279 --> 00:09:09,360
We'd better put in a fake one.

185
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,039
Without seeing the real key,

186
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,799
how could you
make a fake one in advance?

187
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,039
I've got an idea.

188
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:14,759
Good.

189
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,360
Wait for me here tomorrow night.

190
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,799
Someone's here.

191
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:23,080
I asked him over.

192
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:25,120
Seriously?

193
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,120
Your Excellency.

194
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,600
Come in.

195
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:33,159
It's quite late now.

196
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,200
Do you have anything for me?

197
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,679
I have a question for you.

198
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:37,399
Please go ahead.

199
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:41,399
Do you have anything to do with the
Hall of Prayer for Good Harvest?

200
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:44,120
I suppose not.

201
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:46,159
I think so.

202
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:48,879
What's wrong?

203
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:49,480
Nothing.

204
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,320
Take a seat.

205
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:54,120
Your Excellency, thank you.

206
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,200
I might as well stand.

207
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:01,879
Your Excellency,

208
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,919
I heard
that by deterring the Beiqi mission

209
00:10:03,919 --> 00:10:05,480
in the Court of State Ceremonials,

210
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,919
you've made great contributions
to Nanqing.

211
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,039
I will attend the banquet
tomorrow night.

212
00:10:11,279 --> 00:10:12,440
Your Excellency,
charismatic and vigorous as you are,

213
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,200
you'll definitely be promoted
in the near future.

214
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,440
Is this for me?

215
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:15,879
Yes.

216
00:10:16,639 --> 00:10:17,799
Thank you, Your Excellency.

217
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:22,840
Your Excellency,

218
00:10:23,399 --> 00:10:24,799
next time you grant me a reward,

219
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,200
please grant me bank notes instead.

220
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:27,759
They are easier to hide.

221
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:29,639
I want to break into the imperial harem
at night.

222
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,399
Your Excellency,

223
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,320
pardon, please?

224
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,559
I said I want to
break into the imperial harem at night

225
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,919
and sneak into
the Empress Dowager's palace

226
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,279
to steal a key.

227
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:39,399
Of course,

228
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,000
for fear the old lady might notice,

229
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,759
I have to make a fake key overnight

230
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:43,320
to replace the real one.

231
00:10:43,559 --> 00:10:44,639
That's my plan.

232
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,200
Are you kidding me?

233
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:48,840
Not really.

234
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,080
Are you serious?

235
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:51,919
Yes.

236
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:57,159
It's a deadly sin
which could implicate your family.

237
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,120
I suppose it is.

238
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:01,679
Then why do you

239
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:03,120
tell me about it?

240
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,360
I just told you

241
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,080
I have to make a fake key

242
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:06,840
overnight.

243
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:08,399
I have to find
the best locksmith in the capital city.

244
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:10,080
Since I'm not familiar with
the capital city,

245
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,320
I need someone with connections.

246
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,320
That's you.

247
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,720
If I'm involved,

248
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,840
I will also commit a deadly sin.

249
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:22,399
You just find me a locksmith

250
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,240
to make a key.

251
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,440
You know nothing else.

252
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,480
Right!

253
00:11:25,759 --> 00:11:26,919
Then you should only ask me

254
00:11:26,919 --> 00:11:27,720
to find a locksmith.

255
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,279
Right? Why tell me

256
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:29,960
the whole plan?

257
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,440
I also want to tell you less,

258
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:32,759
but I can't.

259
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:35,480
You have to wait for me

260
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,679
outside the imperial palace tomorrow.

261
00:11:38,039 --> 00:11:38,720
Your Excellency!

262
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,919
Aren't you afraid
that I might tell on you?

263
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,519
Do you really want to

264
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,879
trust me

265
00:11:47,879 --> 00:11:48,879
with your life?

266
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:50,200
Of course I do.

267
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:51,960
You're a wise man.

268
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,679
You should know that

269
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:57,000
you only need to
take a little risk by helping me,

270
00:11:57,799 --> 00:12:00,679
but you'll get yourself killed
if you dare betray me.

271
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,000
Why do you say that?

272
00:12:03,919 --> 00:12:04,840
You know how Chen Pingping

273
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,519
treats me.

274
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,919
The Head treats you like his son.

275
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,200
So this is the case.

276
00:12:15,159 --> 00:12:16,320
If I tell on you

277
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,320
and get you killed,

278
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:19,559
the Head will definitely

279
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:21,120
cut me into pieces.

280
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:23,759
You're really wise.

281
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:26,159
Then why don't you ask the Head

282
00:12:26,159 --> 00:12:26,919
to do you the favor.

