00:25:54,640 --> 00:25:56,240
I wonder what they're talking about.

567
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:58,240
It's none of my business.

568
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,440
Your Highness wants to

569
00:26:01,440 --> 00:26:02,359
win Fan Xian over, right?

570
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:06,799
Let's make a bet on

571
00:26:07,599 --> 00:26:10,359
who will get Fan Xian in the end.

572
00:26:14,519 --> 00:26:15,160
What shall we bet?

573
00:26:15,759 --> 00:26:16,440
Life.

574
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:28,160
It seems I've made

575
00:26:28,759 --> 00:26:29,839
an improper joke.

576
00:26:30,519 --> 00:26:32,720
Your Highness, please forgive me!

577
00:26:32,799 --> 00:26:33,400
Fine!

578
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,680
Zhuang Mohan is here.

579
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,680
You've never met Master Zhuang, right?

580
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:17,680
It might be fate

581
00:27:18,559 --> 00:27:19,920
for Beiqi to have

582
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,119
such a literary giant.

583
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:23,880
After explaining classic texts and
annotating articles for decades,

584
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,160
he's got many works to his credit.

585
00:27:32,279 --> 00:27:33,640
In some way,

586
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,839
he's even more powerful than an emperor.

587
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:39,799
Carrying the literary inheritance
all by himself,

588
00:27:44,079 --> 00:27:45,359
doesn't he find it burdensome?

589
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:47,920
If the scholars heard
what you just said,

590
00:27:48,400 --> 00:27:49,960
you would be accused of
disrespect of the saint.

591
00:27:51,079 --> 00:27:51,920
Why would I admit

592
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:52,960
I said those words?

593
00:27:53,720 --> 00:27:55,119
I heard some people

594
00:27:55,119 --> 00:27:56,440
have anchored their hopes on you,

595
00:27:57,039 --> 00:27:58,359
expecting you to become

596
00:27:58,359 --> 00:27:59,759
a literary giant in future.

597
00:28:01,119 --> 00:28:02,839
Your Highness won't hope so for sure!

598
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:07,880
Well, since Master Zhuang is here,

599
00:28:08,359 --> 00:28:09,599
the banquet should start soon.

600
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:10,880
Go back to your seat.

601
00:28:12,079 --> 00:28:13,920
I'm leaving.

602
00:28:15,559 --> 00:28:16,759
I've given you the chance,

603
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:18,720
but you've thrown it away.

604
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:49,000
Here arrives His Majesty!

605
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,119
This way! This way! This way!

606
00:29:06,759 --> 00:29:11,119
May Your Majesty
live ten thousand years!

607
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:15,519
Rise.

608
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,799
Thank you, Your Majesty.

609
00:29:24,799 --> 00:29:26,319
His Majesty has arrived at the
Hall of Prayer for Good Harvest.

610
00:29:29,119 --> 00:29:30,480
Have you checked

611
00:29:31,039 --> 00:29:32,440
all the maidservants,
eunuchs and imperial guards

612
00:29:33,599 --> 00:29:34,480
on shift tonight?

613
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:35,640
Yes, I have.

614
00:29:36,039 --> 00:29:37,160
All of them
have a clean family background.

615
00:29:37,279 --> 00:29:38,279
No one is suspicious.

616
00:29:38,599 --> 00:29:39,400
Among those who entered the Hall,

617
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,960
have you found anyone suspicious?

618
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:41,680
Yes,

619
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:43,680
Fan Xian is.

620
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:45,200
According to
the Division of Imperial Guards,

621
00:29:45,440 --> 00:29:46,720
he carried a dagger and poisons with him

622
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:49,079
when he arrived.

623
00:29:52,519 --> 00:29:53,400
What about Zhuang Mohan?

624
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,640
Zhuang Mohan only took inside

625
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:56,000
a roll of old paper.

626
00:29:56,440 --> 00:29:57,680
My men took the chance to check it.

627
00:29:57,799 --> 00:29:58,839
There was nothing inside.

628
00:30:00,559 --> 00:30:01,519
I think

629
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,039
Zhuang Mohan doesn't practice

630
00:30:03,039 --> 00:30:03,960
martial arts.

631
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,559
He wouldn't be a problem.

632
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:10,440
Yun Zhilan went inside with his sword.

633
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,039
Right.

634
00:30:12,359 --> 00:30:15,759
But Yun Zhilan is
an apprentice of Si Gujian.

635
00:30:16,039 --> 00:30:17,119
He is not supposed to

636
00:30:17,359 --> 00:30:18,880
know Zhuang Mohan.

637
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,240
If Yun Zhilan tries to

638
00:30:22,319 --> 00:30:23,480
kill His Majesty with his sword,

639
00:30:23,480 --> 00:30:24,240
who can stop him?

640
00:30:24,839 --> 00:30:27,599
Eunuch Hong Sixiang
is right outside the Hall.

641
00:30:30,039 --> 00:30:32,160
Serve the dishes.

642
00:30:46,359 --> 00:30:47,920
Eunuch Hong, it's a night owl.

643
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:19,480
Chief Musician Fan.

644
00:31:21,480 --> 00:31:23,039
Your Excellency Fan,
His Majesty is calling you.

645
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:25,000
Calling me?

646
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,839
What does His Majesty call me?

647
00:31:27,039 --> 00:31:28,440
You're the Chief Musician of
the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

648
00:31:28,440 --> 00:31:29,359
That's the name
of your official position.

649
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,279
Your Majesty.

650
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:41,920
You've seen me a few times,
but you've never knelt down.

651
00:31:43,839 --> 00:31:46,839
I thought
you would remain standing this time.

652
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:49,119
Then I would piss off everyone.

653
00:32:00,319 --> 00:32:02,720
Look at your blurred eyes.

654
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,720
You must have drunk a lot.

655
00:32:05,599 --> 00:32:06,400
Your Majesty,

656
