On such a big occasion,

657
00:32:08,720 --> 00:32:10,440
I can't help feeling nervous.

658
00:32:12,279 --> 00:32:12,880
Yun Zhilan?

659
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,920
Your two apprentices

660
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:19,240
were killed by him.

661
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:21,799
I know.

662
00:32:22,519 --> 00:32:23,680
Young as he is,

663
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,519
he's somewhat competent.

664
00:32:31,279 --> 00:32:33,720
He's competent if he can kill me.

665
00:32:36,839 --> 00:32:38,920
The apprentice of Si Gujian

666
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,920
is really proud.

667
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:55,119
I get that.

668
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:00,559
Fan Xian.

669
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,680
According to the memorial submitted
by Court of State Ceremonials,

670
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:06,359
you've done a great job this time.

671
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,200
The war was started because of you,

672
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:09,079
and it was ended by you.

673
00:33:09,079 --> 00:33:12,000
I don't want to praise you in public.

674
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:15,160
Come on! Join me for a drink.

675
00:33:32,079 --> 00:33:33,160
Chief Musician Fan, please wait.

676
00:33:37,720 --> 00:33:39,960
Your Majesty, I have something to say.

677
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:40,880
Go ahead.

678
00:33:41,279 --> 00:33:42,680
Besides being good at martial arts,

679
00:33:42,839 --> 00:33:44,200
Fan Xian is also famous for
literary grace.

680
00:33:44,599 --> 00:33:45,880
I'm amazed by his talents

681
00:33:45,880 --> 00:33:46,920
in writing poems.

682
00:33:47,119 --> 00:33:48,039
Recently, I've heard that

683
00:33:48,319 --> 00:33:49,279
when negotiating with Beiqi,

684
00:33:49,279 --> 00:33:50,880
Fan Xian handled it properly without
being too humble or too pushy.

685
00:33:51,039 --> 00:33:52,599
He can be entrusted
with important tasks.

686
00:33:54,559 --> 00:33:55,480
Just go straight to the point.

687
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,119
Why not put Fan Xian in charge of

688
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,279
the imperial examinations next spring?

689
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,720
Scholars going down in history

690
00:34:04,799 --> 00:34:07,400
under the supervision of a youth talent,

691
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,599
it might become a much told tale.

692
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:13,320
Though Fan Xian is known for his poems,

693
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:16,000
he is inexperienced after all.

694
00:34:19,559 --> 00:34:20,079
Your Majesty.

695
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,559
Though inexperienced,

696
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:23,679
he is really talented.

697
00:34:24,320 --> 00:34:25,039
I agree.

698
00:34:25,519 --> 00:34:27,840
to put Fan Xian in charge of
the imperial examinations held in spring.

699
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:30,079
Well...

700
00:34:30,079 --> 00:34:31,159
How could this be?

701
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:39,760
There're still a few months
before the imperial examinations.

702
00:34:41,039 --> 00:34:42,119
We'll see by then.

703
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:44,119
You may all leave.

704
00:34:48,599 --> 00:34:49,159
Your Majesty.

705
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:53,360
Is this young man Fan Xian?

706
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:56,000
Master Zhuang,
have you also heard of him?

707
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,480
I've read his poem.

708
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,440
Young as he is,

709
00:34:59,719 --> 00:35:00,880
he's talented in poetry.

710
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:04,280
Master Zhuang, you should guide and
support the younger generation.

711
00:35:05,199 --> 00:35:08,239
I'm a minister from Beiqi.

712
00:35:09,519 --> 00:35:12,440
I should not interfere with
the political affairs of Nanqing.

713
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:15,519
But the imperial examinations
held in spring

714
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:18,199
are of fundamental importance

715
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,599
to scholars around the world.

716
00:35:21,079 --> 00:35:22,519
You should be cautious

717
00:35:23,239 --> 00:35:24,719
when choosing the man in charge.

718
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,840
Master Zhuang, you're absolutely right.

719
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,159
When it comes to
the imperial examinations,

720
00:35:30,400 --> 00:35:33,119
we can't be too cautious.

721
00:35:42,519 --> 00:35:44,159
Master Zhuang, I admire you for being
well versed in the learning of

722
00:35:45,159 --> 00:35:46,360
both ancient and modern times,

723
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:50,280
but I don't agree with
what you just said.

724
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:53,280
Though I'm a woman

725
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,440
with little knowledge,

726
00:35:55,199 --> 00:35:57,239
I've read the seven-character poem
written by Fan Xian.

727
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:59,159
He's young indeed,

728
00:35:59,599 --> 00:36:00,920
but this poem alone

729
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:03,000
can show he's really talented.

730
00:36:04,159 --> 00:36:05,719
What you said just now

731
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:07,280
is secretly against Fan Xian.

732
00:36:07,719 --> 00:36:08,599
Are you afraid that

733
00:36:08,599 --> 00:36:10,199
this young man might surpass you one day

734
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:11,960
and gain a better reputation than you?

735
00:36:18,039 --> 00:36:20,840
Everyone else present here
is either a trustworthy minister

736
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:22,320
or a learned scholar.

737
00:36:23,119 --> 00:36:24,639
They certainly don't like to argue.

738
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,320
Ignorant as I am,

739
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:29,679
I'm willing to speak up for

740
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:31,119
our talent of Nanqing.

741
00:36:32,599 --> 00:36:35,079
Are you referring to
that seven-character poem?

742
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:36,960
Exactly.

743
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:40,599
Master, have you got any poem

744
00:36:40,599 --> 00:36:42,559
better than that?

745
00:36:42,559 --> 00:36:45,559
Yunrui, mind your manners in the Hall.

746
00:36:49,119 --> 00:36:50,639
Master Zhuang, you're broad-minded.

747
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:53,639
Please forgive her for being rude.

748
00:36:59,239 --> 00:37:02,800
The wind so swift,
the sky so wide, apes wail and cry;

749
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:08,079
Water so clear and beach so white,
birds wheel and fly.

750
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:11,559
The boundless forest sheds its leaves
shower by shower;

751
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:16,000
The endless river rolls its waves
hour after hour.

752
00:37:17,199 --> 00:37:21,119
A thousand miles from home,
I'm grieved at autumn's plight;

753
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:25,599
Ill now and then for years,
alone I'm on this height.

754
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:31,239
Living in times so hard,
at frosted hair I pine;

755
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:38,440
Cast down by poverty,
I have to give up wine.

756
00:37:41,639 --> 00:37:43,199
What a fantastic poem!

757
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,480
I've written poems my whole life,

758
00:37:45,679 --> 00:37:47,039
but none

759
00:37:47,239 --> 00:37:48,960
can match that.

760
00:37:50,119 --> 00:37:50,920
In this case,

761
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:53,360
you admit defeat candidly.

762
00:37:54,119 --> 00:37:56,440
The first four lines are wonderful.

763
00:37:57,239 --> 00:37:58,400
But people all say

764
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,320
the essence of the poem

765
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:01,480
is the latter four lines.

766
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:04,639
The latter four lines
are absolutely marvelous.

767
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:07,920
It's a pity that

768
00:38:10,239 --> 00:38:12,280
they were not written by Mr. Fan.

769
00:38:13,519 --> 00:38:15,320
So Fan Xian copied the poem.

770
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:18,360
Yes.

771
00:38:24,320 --> 00:38:26,480
I also find it strange.

772
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:27,760
How could he

773
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:29,000
be so talented?

774
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:31,639
Fan Xian,

775
00:38:34,239 --> 00:38:35,559
do you have anything to say?

776
00:38:36,519 --> 00:38:37,679
Master Zhuang can say

777
00:38:37,679 --> 00:38:38,519
whatever he likes

778
00:38:38,519 --> 00:38:40,519
After all,
highly respected as Master Zhuang,

779
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:42,840
what he says counts even
if he has no proof.

780
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:44,199
Your Majesty,

781
00:38:44,559 --> 00:38:45,639
I can prove that

782
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:46,920
Fan Xian wrote the poem
at the poetry gathering

783
00:38:47,199 --> 00:38:48,800
held in Prince Jing's mansion.

784
00:38:49,679 --> 00:38:51,239
Guo Baokun, the Imperial Compiler

785
00:38:51,239 --> 00:38:52,320
was also there.

786
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:54,079
He can be a witness.

787
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:56,360
Is Guo Baokun here?

788
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:57,000
Yes, Your Majesty.

789
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:07,039
Did Fan Xian write the poem?

790
00:39:10,440 --> 00:39:11,159
Yes.

791
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:12,800
In this case,

792
00:39:13,159 --> 00:39:15,119
Master Zhuang is trying to
frame Fan Xian up on purpose.

793
00:39:15,599 --> 00:39:17,360
He might be misled by others

794
00:39:18,039 --> 00:39:20,119
to form such a misunderstanding.

795
00:39:26,199 --> 00:39:27,599
What a coincidence!

796
00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:29,360
The latter four lines of the poem

797
00:39:30,039 --> 00:39:31,400
were written by my teacher

798
00:39:31,679 --> 00:39:33,199
when he was visiting Tingzhou.

799
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:37,239
It should to be a good thing to see

800
00:39:37,599 --> 00:39:40,360
such wonderful lines reappearing
in the world.

801
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:42,039
But Mr. Fan

802
00:39:42,400 --> 00:39:44,480
actually made a name with other's poem.

803
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:47,199
Is that appropriate?

804
00:39:50,239 --> 00:39:54,000
For scholars,
morality is more important than talent.

805
00:39:56,679 --> 00:39:58,519
The first four lines of the poem

806
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:00,840
are remarkable.

807
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:03,679
Mr. Fan is definitely talented.

808
00:40:04,519 --> 00:40:07,400
But why does he have to be so greedy

809
00:40:07,679 --> 00:40:09,280
as to make a name

810
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:11,320
with other's work.

811
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,360
I was hesitant about

812
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:18,559
telling the truth.

813
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:21,440
But after careful thinking,

814
00:40:23,519 --> 00:40:25,000
I feel that by telling the truth,

815
00:40:25,679 --> 00:40:27,199
I might help Mr. Fan

816
00:40:27,199 --> 00:40:28,440
and decided to
return to the correct path.

817
00:40:29,119 --> 00:40:32,360
There's no making without breaking.

818
00:40:32,639 --> 00:40:35,719
He can focus on moral cultivation
in future.

819
00:40:36,119 --> 00:40:37,119
Mr. Fan,

820
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:39,599
I told the truth

821
00:40:39,599 --> 00:40:41,159
because I cherish your talents.

822
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:43,000
I mean no harm.

823
00:40:43,719 --> 00:40:46,559
Please be introspective.

824
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:47,840
Fan Xian,

825
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:50,199
feel free to speak your mind.

826
00:40:51,239 --> 00:40:52,039
Master Zhuang,

827
00:40:53,719 --> 00:40:55,079
is your teacher surnamed Du?

828
00:40:56,159 --> 00:40:57,880
No.

829
00:40:59,519 --> 00:41:00,360
Never mind.

830
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:03,559
Master Zhuang is known for

831
00:41:03,559 --> 00:41:04,960
respecting teachers and honoring truth,

832
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:07,199
I suppose
he won't use his teacher's reputation

833
00:41:07,199 --> 00:41:08,199
to frame up an innocent man.

834
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:11,039
But men are hard to predict.

835
00:41:12,039 --> 00:41:14,920
He might feel unhappy

836
00:41:15,400 --> 00:41:18,079
seeing a young man rising to his fame

837
00:41:18,599 --> 00:41:21,480
and make all this up to
destroy his future.

